QueenSkiilia Mobile App — Development Todo
==========================================

Reference plan files: mobile development plan/00–07
Stack: Expo SDK 54 · Expo Router v6 · React 19 + React Compiler · RN 0.81 New Arch
       TanStack Query (NOT Apollo) · fetch API (NOT axios) · NativeTabs · inline styles


